<span id="freeTextContainer6610088309633617142">I buy none of the characters Melville, and that is a first with you. The story is there though and it was a good adventure story - Sir Walter could have told it better, and that too is a first with you. But, despite the cribs, the foretopman and the motley crew will stay with me, but not for the telling.<br/><br/><i>Adieu, Rights of Man!</i> No irony intended, only Paine! Or not.</span>

